description:
Popular arrangements of six songs from Touhou: Palace of the Earth Spirits, accompanied by six challenge stages
are all compiled into this "Touhou Chireiden Arrangements Pack"!
ShinRa-Bansho, TamaOnSen, A-One, IOSYS, BUTAOTOME, Demetori—it's a deluxe compilation of Touhou's most popular faces!
We're so excited to share these new recordings with you!

This pack contains the following:

■6 Songs
・Spider's Blood / A-One / Original Song: The Dark Blowhole , The Sealed-Away Youkai ~ Lost Place
・Yukemuri TamaOnSen / TamaOnSen / Original Song: Walking the Streets of a Former Hell
・The fear is oneself / BUTAOTOME / Original Song: Satori Maiden　～ 3rd Eye
・The Ultimate Yakiniku Restaurant! Orin's Jigokutei! / IOSYS / Original Song: Lullaby of Deserted Hell / Corpse Voyage ~ Be of good cheer!
・Solar Sect of Mystic Wisdom　~ Nuclear Fusion / Demetori / Original Song: Solar Sect of Mystic Wisdom　~ Nuclear Fusion
・An Unconscious Requiem / Shinra-Bansho / Original Song: Youkai Girl of Hartmann

■6 Challenge Stages
・Lv4 See Here! My Kappa Is A Genius (Spider's Blood)
・Lv5 Take Your Complaints to The Manager (Yukemuri TamaOnSen)
・Lv6 Marisa's Success Story (The fear is oneself)
・Lv8 This Meat Is FIRE (The Ultimate Yakiniku Restaurant! Orin's Jigokutei!)
・Lv9 The Fastest Ever! (Solar Sect of Mystic Wisdom ~ Nuclear Fusion)
・Lv10 So Hey, I... (An Unconscious Requiem)

*Internet connection required for purchase.
* Game must be restarted after songs are purchased in order to use them.
name: Touhou Chireiden Arrangements Pack
